title: TagMap Test

This tiddler is tagged with all five categories so the Tag Map tab shows five columns.

Open the info panel and switch to the //Tag Map// tab. Items with `list-before` show a ↑ badge; items with `list-after` show a ↓ badge. Hover the badge to see the field value (or the field name if the value is empty).
